dict.string: search through 2500+ mind maps on the web
go inside any of the mind maps

IFS=$'\n'
echo "<?xml version='1.0'?><items>" for line in $(grep --extended-regexp '\[.+\]\(.+\)' < "$mdfile"); do sed -E "s|.*\[(.+)\]\((.+)\).*|<item arg='\2' valid='yes'><title>\1</title></item>|" <<< "${line}" done echo "</items>"
